<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Ella Rises – Empowering Young Women</title>

<!-- Bootstrap -->
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

<!-- Google Fonts -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
  :root {
    --cream: #f9f5ea;
    --light-pink: #ffd8d1;
    --pink: #f9afb1;
    --sage: #9ab59d;
    --gray: #3a3f3b;
    --coral: #f4b092;
    --rose: #ce325b;
  }

  body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    background-color: var(--light-pink);
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    color: var(--gray);
  }

  /* NAVBAR */
  .navbar-custom {
    background-color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .navbar-brand {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    color: var(--gray) !important;
  }

  .navbar-links a {
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 15px;
    color: var(--gray);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .navbar-links a:hover,
  .nav-right a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .nav-right a {
    margin-left: 15px;
    color: var(--gray);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* HERO SECTION */
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 140px 20px 120px;
    background-color: var(--light-pink);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--gray);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-buttons .btn {
    margin: 8px;
    padding: 12px 28px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    border-radius: 25px;
  }

  .btn-white {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--gray);
    color: var(--gray);
  }
  .btn-white:hover {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .btn-donate {
    background: var(--rose);
    color: white;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn-donate:hover {
    background: #b42b50;
  }

  /* CURVED SECTION WRAPPERS */
  .section-wrapper {
    background: white;
    padding: 80px 20px;
    border-top-left-radius: 100px;
    border-top-right-radius: 100px;
    margin-top: -50px;
  }

  /* GENERIC SECTION */
  .section-title {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  /* IMAGE PLACEHOLDERS */
.img-placeholder {
    width: 100%;             /* Make image fill the width of the white card */
    height: 200px;           /* FORCE all images to be the same height */
    object-fit: cover;       /* The Magic Line: Crops the image so it doesn't squish */
    border: none;            /* Removes the dotted border */
    border-radius: 10px;     /* Rounds the corners to look nice */
    display: block;          /* Required for centering */
    margin: 0 auto;          /* Centers the image horizontally */
}

  /* PROGRAM CARDS */
  .program-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 25px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    height: 100%;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .program-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }
  .program-card h4 {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    margin-top: 15px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
    height: 100px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .footer-text {
    font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .copyright {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 8px 0 20px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- NAVBAR -->
<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-custom fixed-top">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="navbar-brand">
      Ella
      <img src="/fulllogo.jpg" alt="Ella Rises Logo" style="width:35px; height:35px; object-fit: contain; vertical-align: text-bottom; margin-left: 8px;">
      Rises
    </span>

    <div class="navbar-links mx-auto d-none d-lg-flex" style="position: absolute; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);">
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="/donate">Donate</a>
    </div>

    <div class="nav-right d-none d-lg-flex" style="flex: 0 0 auto; margin-left: auto;">

      <% if (!isLoggedIn) { %>
          <!-- SHOW WHEN LOGGED OUT -->
          <a href="/login">Login</a>
      <% } else { %>
          <!-- SHOW WHEN LOGGED IN -->
          <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
          <a href="/userDashboard">View Dashboard</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>


<!-- HERO / WELCOME SECTION -->
<section class="hero">
    <h1>Together We Are</h1>
    <h1>Ella Rises</h1>
    <h4>Inviting young women to pursue higher education and embrace their heritage</h4>
    <h4>by providing culturally rooted programs and educational experiences.</h4>

  <div class="hero-buttons">
    <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-donate">Donate</a>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- EVENTS SECTION -->
<div class="section-wrapper">
<section id="events" class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">Upcoming Events</h2>

  <% if (events && events.length > 0) { %>

    <div class="row g-4">

      <% events.forEach(event => { %>
      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="program-card p-3 text-center">

          <h4 class="mt-2"><%= event.EventName %></h4>

          <p class="text-muted mb-1">
            <strong>Date:</strong>
            <%= new Date(event.EventDateTimeStart).toLocaleDateString() %>
          </p>

          <p class="text-muted mb-1">
            <strong>Time:</strong>
            <%= new Date(event.EventDateTimeStart).toLocaleTimeString([], { hour:'numeric', minute:'2-digit' }) %> – 
            <%= new Date(event.EventDateTimeEnd).toLocaleTimeString([], { hour:'numeric', minute:'2-digit' }) %>
          </p>

          <p class="text-muted">
            <strong>Location:</strong> <%= event.EventLocation %>
          </p>

        </div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>

    </div>

  <% } else { %>

    <!-- No Events Message -->
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-4">
      <div class="program-card p-4 text-center" style="max-width: 450px;">

        <h4 class="mb-2">No Upcoming Events</h4>

        <p class="text-muted">
          There aren’t any events scheduled right now.<br>
          Please check back soon!
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>

  <% } %>

</section>
</div>



<!-- PROGRAMS SECTION -->
<div class="section-wrapper" style="background-color: var(--cream);">
<section id="programs" class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">Our Programs</h2>

  <div class="row g-4">

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
      <div class="program-card">
        <!-- Anders putting in images -->
        <img src="/BalletImage.jpeg" alt="Ballet Event" class="img-placeholder">
        <h4>Ballet Folklorico</h4>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
      <div class="program-card">
        <!-- Anders putting in images -->
        <img src="/Mariachi.jpeg" alt="Mariachi Event" class="img-placeholder">
        <h4>Mariachi</h4>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
      <div class="program-card">
        <!-- Anders putting in images -->
        <img src="/SummitImage.jpg" alt="Summit Event" class="img-placeholder">
        <h4>Summit + Educational Pathways</h4>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3">
      <div class="program-card">
        <!-- Anders putting in images -->
        <img src="/SteamImage.jpeg" alt="STEAM Event" class="img-placeholder">
        <h4>STEAM</h4>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 text-center" style="max-width: 850px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      The majority of the young women that we serve come from multicultural backgrounds, and it's important to give them an opportunity to experience things that they might otherwise not be experiencing because they don't have family members in these career paths, or they might not have mentors in their lives who are pursuing or working in these careers.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
</div>


<!-- DONATION SECTION -->
<div class="section-wrapper">
<section id="donate" class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">Support Our Mission</h2>

  <!-- Anders putting in images -->
  <img src="/Donate.jpeg" alt="Donate" class="img-placeholder">

  <!-- THANK YOU CONTENT -->
  <div class="mt-5 text-center" style="max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <h3 class="mt-5" style="font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;">Thank You</h3>
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      A big thank you to our supporters who make it possible for us to accomplish our
      goals and provide these wonderful programs for our young women!
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="text-center mt-4">
    <a href="/donate" class="btn btn-donate">Donate Now</a>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-5 text-center" style="max-width: 750px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
    <p style="font-size: 1.1rem;">
      Your generous contributions have lasting impact.
    </p>
  </div>

</section>
</div>


<!-- ABOUT SECTION -->
<div class="section-wrapper" id="about" style="background-color: var(--cream);">
<section class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">About Ella Rises</h2>

  <div class="mx-auto text-center" style="max-width: 800px; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
    <p>
      Ella Rises empowers young women to pursue higher education while celebrating the richness of their cultural heritage.
    </p>

    <p>
      Many of the girls we serve come from multicultural backgrounds and may not have mentors, family members, or role models working in the careers they dream about. We exist to bridge that gap. Through ARIs, we open doors to experiences and opportunities that these young women might not otherwise have access to—and we bring those possibilities directly into their community.
    </p>

    <p>
      Adolescence can feel confusing, isolating, and uncertain. For a young woman navigating middle school or high school, it's not always clear where she fits or who she can become. ARIs creates a space where she is seen, supported, and surrounded by a community that believes in her potential.
    </p>

    <p>
      A major pillar of Ella Rises grew from the lived experiences of first-generation college students. And today, most of the young women we serve are the first in their families to pursue higher education. That journey is challenging—but it becomes powerful when walked together.
    </p>

    <p>
      At Ella Rises, we don't just support the girls—we support their families. Grandparents, siblings, brothers, and parents are welcomed into the experience. Together, we build a community that celebrates culture, embraces education, and lifts young women to rise.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
</div>


<!-- FOOTER -->
<div class="footer">
  <div class="footer-text">
    Ella 
    <img src="/EllaRises.jpg" alt="Logo" style="width:30px; height:auto; vertical-align: middle;">
    Rises
  </div>
</div>

<p class="copyright">© 2025 Ella Rises. All Rights Reserved.</p>

<!-- Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
